It is important to me to work daily on my HEART POWER!!!! Heart power isn't always #xoxo 😙😙😙😙 and #flowers 💐💐💐💐. It's about the willingness to see the things that are important to the people in my life. It's giving my undivided attention when a friend needs to vent; it's about listening and not trying to give advice that I wouldn't take myself🙄🙄; it's figuring out how I can give support; it's setting my pride aside to be there even when we have disagreements; it's showing up & being present in the moment; saying I'm sorry, saying I didn't have bad intentions; it's talking things out when deep in my bones my body tries to pull away. HEART POWER is knowing that I am not the only person on this planet 🌎  with needs. HEART POWER is my purpose!!! 💜💜💜💜💜💜💜💜💜💜😘😘😘😘😘😘😘😘😘😘 #wemaplove #journeygirl #heart #power #relationship #relationships #couples #friends #family #happy #dailyinspiration #inspire #love #bebold #beautiful #wednesday #mindbodysoul #motivate #change #positiveenergy #positivity #mindset #mindfulness #spirit #powerful

So that your understanding becomes perfect, consider that your heart is both good and evil. You ask, “What? Should I also live evil?” The spirit of the depths demands: “The life that you could still live, you should live. Well-being decides, not your well-being, not the well-being of the others, but only well-being.” ~ Carl Gustav Jung. 1875-1961. Liber Novus - The Red Book.
